{"tid":870482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"網購迷藥姦兩小鮮肉學徒　酒店師傅囚3年4月","createTime":"2018-10-21T07:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T07:49:38.000Z","uid":145999,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"697654c28f718a332c6ce1c83afa17c5d29536a1","tid":870482,"uid":145999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"浙江杭州一名40多歲的酒店職員早年離婚後，竟迷上小鮮肉，還利用師傅身份迷姦兩名學徒。他周五（19日）因犯強制猥褻罪成，被富陽區法院被判監3年4個月。 <br />\n<br />\n兩名分別王姓及張姓的男子在當地酒店任職學徒，與鄧姓師傅住在酒店同一間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。去年6月以來，王男發現身體異常，起床後常見頭暈，加上肛門隱隱作痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，便到醫院檢查，驗身結果卻顯示正常。他與張男閒聊時，竟發現兩人有相同的症狀。王男遂將情況告知鄧男，但對方卻指可能是工作辛苦，身體勞累所致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 <br />\n<br />\n直到今年初，富陽區警方收到寄自陜西省公安廳的一份協助調查報告，指陜西警方破獲了一個出售「九代水」迷藥的集團，並發現已有迷藥流入富陽，今年4月，警察到鄧男工作的酒店調查，鄧男才承認曾於網上購買「九代水」，再落在王、張二人的飲料中，待他們失去意識後再迷姦。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181020/mobile/bkn-20181020144541647-1020_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181020%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181020144541647-1020_00952_001.html&d=NZ0CFHb0uuKSrsDB%2FSRqOU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=12ac64b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181020/mobile/bkn-20181020144541647-1020_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"30e913155943d1f06da55fa367acc0d9698f9173","tid":870482,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:19:53.000Z","msg":"工作辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1dee6b63a37e8397a5755602d8ce144b2369e7","tid":870482,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:29:34.000Z","msg":"肛門隱隱作痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74918f1bf83f498b58d1b3dc95d29a886d55159a","tid":870482,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f515467367cabeaf2c229a4ac0eda663e05cd527","tid":870482,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:49:38.000Z","msg":"佢地唔會覺得屙屎暢順左好多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}